children.content: We all have the power to live more sustainably and make a difference, no matter where we are. Need help getting started? We have you covered. Here are three ways to make more sustainable choices with Google in 2022.

1 Google Nest Thermostat: Conserve energy while you're away from home. Since 2011, Nest thermostats have saved over 80 billion kWh of energy and counting  enough to power 23 million electric cars for a year. Start the year on a sustainable note by setting up eco-temps and enabling Home and Away routines.
2 Google Flights: Find more sustainable travel options on Google Flights  youll see the estimated emissions listed under each flight.

3 Google Maps: See the most fuel efficient route on your next drive with eco-friendly routing on Google Maps. Explore relative fuel savings and the ETA difference between routes, then choose the one that works best for you.
What are your sustainability goals for 2022? Let us know below!
